{
  "chapter": 25,
  "chapter_summary": "小方凌晨从柳巷醉酒醒来，遇到一个衣着褴褛但机灵老成的小孩。小孩手捧装满小虫的铁皮罐子，自称是鸟的朋友。小孩受一位神秘朋友之托，前来带小方去见面，但拒绝透露对方身份。小孩带小方穿过人群，来到大昭寺。在一幅罗刹鬼女吸人脑髓的恐怖壁画前，小孩要求小方立下毒誓保守秘密。随后二人来到建在山岩上的鸟房，那里屋檐下挂满精巧的鸟笼，门常开不锁。木屋内，一个背影瘦削、双肩斜削、落寞萧索的人背对门坐在火盆旁。小方从未见过此人，心中疑虑——这个人究竟是谁？为什么要冒称他的朋友？",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这些是什么虫？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_hai",
      "speaker_name": "小孩",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "这些不是虫。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_xiao_hai",
      "text": "不是虫？不是虫是什么？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_hai",
      "speaker_name": "小孩",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "在你眼中看来虽然是虫，可是在我的朋友眼中看来，却是顿丰富的大餐。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_xiao_hai",
      "text": "你明明是个人，为什么要跟鸟交朋友？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 37
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_hai",
      "speaker_name": "小孩",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "因为没有人肯跟我交朋友，只有鸟肯跟我交朋友。有朋友总比没有朋友好。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 41
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错，有朋友的确比没有朋友好。鸟朋友有时候也比人朋友好。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 49
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_hai",
      "speaker_name": "小孩",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_xiao_hai",
      "text": "因为人会骗人，会害人，鸟不会。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_hai",
      "speaker_name": "小孩",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "你呢？你对朋友好不好？如果你有个朋友需要你帮助，想要你去看看他，你肯不肯去？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 61
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_xiao_hai",
      "text": "如果我肯去，可怎么样？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_hai",
      "speaker_name": "小孩",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "你肯去，现在就跟我走。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_xiao_hai",
      "text": "跟你走？为什么要跟你走？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_hai",
      "speaker_name": "小孩",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "因为我就是你那个朋友叫我来找你的。我已经在这里等了你一夜。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 71
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_xiao_hai",
      "text": "你知道我是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_hai",
      "speaker_name": "小孩",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "我当然知道。你姓方，别人都叫你要命的小方。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_xiao_hai",
      "text": "我那个朋友是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_hai",
      "speaker_name": "小孩",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "我不能说。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_xiao_hai",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_hai",
      "speaker_name": "小孩",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "因为他要我替他保守秘密，我已经答应了他。就算你杀了我，我也不会说出来的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 87
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_xiao_hai",
      "text": "好。我跟你去，现在就去。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_hai",
      "speaker_name": "小孩",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "我能替你的朋友保守秘密，你呢？你能不能替朋友保守秘密？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 101
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_hai",
      "speaker_name": "小孩",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "你跟我来！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 107
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_xiao_hai",
      "text": "这里是什么地方？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_hai",
      "speaker_name": "小孩",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "是大昭寺。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_hai",
      "speaker_name": "小孩",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "你知不知道这个人是谁？这个罗刹鬼女为什么要吸他的脑？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 155
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_hai",
      "speaker_name": "小孩",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "因为他是个不守信的人。他答应为他的朋友保守秘密，却没有做到。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 161
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_xiao_hai",
      "text": "你好像不太相信我。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_hai",
      "speaker_name": "小孩",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "我们还不是朋友，我不能信任你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_hai",
      "speaker_name": "小孩",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "你要我带你去，一定要在这里先立个誓，如果你违背了誓言，终生都要像这个人一样，受罗刹鬼女恶毒的折磨。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 171
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_hai",
      "speaker_name": "小孩",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "你果然是个好人。现在我真的带你去了。",
      "tone": "欣慰",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_xiao_hai",
      "text": "到哪里去？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_hai",
      "speaker_name": "小孩",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "到鸟房去。你的朋友和我的朋友都在那里。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_hai",
      "speaker_name": "小孩",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "这些鸟笼都是我做的。你看不看得出它们有什么特别地方？",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 197
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_hai",
      "speaker_name": "小孩",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "我不愿把它们当囚犯一样关在笼子里，只要它们高兴，随时都可以飞出去。可是飞走的往往又会飞回来。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_hai",
      "speaker_name": "小孩",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "因为它们也知道我是它们的朋友。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 207
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_xiao_hai",
      "text": "我那个朋友呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_hai",
      "speaker_name": "小孩",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "你的朋友就在里面。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 212
    }
